&lt;h2&gt;What We&#39;re About&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apiiro is the Agentic AppSec Platform built to transform how development teams design, develop, and deliver secure software. Powered by Deep Code Analysis, we give security and engineering teams the risk context they need to ship fast without cutting corners. As pioneers in ASPM, we&#39;re not just keeping up with the AI era. We&#39;re defining what secure development looks like inside it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;About the Team&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our AI team operates at the intersection of agentic AI and application security, owning the development of AI-powered capabilities within Apiiro&#39;s ASPM platform. We move ideas from early experimentation all the way to production — and keep them running reliably once they&#39;re there. As a cross-functional team of engineers, data scientists, and analysts, we turn cutting-edge ML and agentic AI into scalable, real-world features that power the platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You Will Do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;padding-left: 0; margin-left: 0;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and ship end-to-end AI-driven features and agentic workflows- from experimentation through validation to production deployment (Python and C#).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design scalable backend services that support production-grade agentic AI capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and improve solutions powered by LLMs, AI agents, multi-agent systems, and generative AI frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate agentic architectures and model performance, owning monitoring, reliability, and continuous improvement in production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with software engineers, data scientists, and analysts to drive AI innovation across the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You&#39;re About&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;padding-left: 0; margin-left: 0;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of hands-on backend software engineering experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;B.Sc. in Computer Science or equivalent practical experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience building LLM-powered applications, AI agents, or generative AI systems using modern AI/ML frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-driven and comfortable operating in a fast-paced environment — you don&#39;t wait to be told what to do next.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong collaborator with clear communication skills; you thrive in diverse, cross-functional teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with multi-agent architectures or agentic evaluation frameworks &lt;em&gt;(preferred)&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with C# or polyglot engineering environments &lt;em&gt;(a plus)&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What We Stand For at Apiiro&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer-First.&lt;/strong&gt; Our customers are partners, not just clients. We anticipate their needs, go above and beyond to prove business outcomes, and measure our success by theirs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Excellence Mindset.&lt;/strong&gt; We set the bar high, embrace challenges with curiosity, and never settle. Good enough isn&#39;t in our vocabulary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OneTeam.&lt;/strong&gt; One mission, collective ownership, no silos. Our strength is in how we show up for each other and for our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accountability.&lt;/strong&gt; We own our actions, our commitments, and our results. Integrity and follow-through are built-in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Most companies react to security. We believe it should be built in from the start. If that mission resonates, let&#39;s talk.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

