&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Apiiro is a fast-growing startup at the forefront of the Application Security field. Our cutting-edge platform is designed to help development teams build secure software quickly, enabling them to move faster while managing risks. As pioneers in the app-sec space, we’re shaping the future of secure software development. If you&#39;re looking for an exciting opportunity to make a significant impact and grow with a passionate team, Apiiro is the place to be.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You: The Solution-Oriented Innovator&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Depth &amp;amp; Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; With 5+ years in backend or server-side development, you’re experienced in building complex systems from scratch and driving them through every phase, from architecture to deployment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative Problem Solver:&lt;/strong&gt; You thrive on tackling tough challenges with fresh ideas, devising clever solutions for new, unfamiliar problems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborative by Nature:&lt;/strong&gt; You enjoy working in fast-paced, collaborative environments, bringing out the best in yourself and others as part of a talented team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; Background in algorithm development, ML models, Docker, Kubernetes, cloud technologies, Infrastructure as Code (IaC), DevOps, and CI/CD tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Academic Background:&lt;/strong&gt; B.Sc. in Computer Science or equivalent experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Role: Drive, Build, and Shape&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build Scalable Solutions:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop a robust, scalable system using a mix of languages, frameworks, and machine learning models. You’ll take full ownership of features, guiding them from idea to live product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer-Centric Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate directly with customers to understand their needs and integrate valuable insights into your work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Disciplinary Innovation:&lt;/strong&gt; Engage in initiatives across various tech domains — from DevOps and infrastructure to data engineering and full-stack development — expanding your impact company-wide.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
